Title: PLAYING CS:GO THEN vs NOW
Description: In the video, I show with a simple meme I made using the Doomer from this video (https://youtu.be/6wybSxuaeUY) an interesting and quite common phenomenon in the world of competitive gaming.  Back in the day when we started playing a game, in this case, CS:GO, the gameplay was fun even though we weren't the best.  Getting better brought huge satisfaction and joy.  However, once we reached a really high level, the game became way less enjoyable.
